Sentencas: Some diffraction streaks along [200] and [112] patterns in HR-TEM appeared for the ordering of oxygen vacancies, or as the overlap of B-site cations (Co2+/Co(3+)and Mn2+/Mn3+) with stacking fault-derived scattering of ordering.

Sentencas: Area-specific resistance (ASR) was 0.023 omega cm(2)when Nd(0.5)Sr(0.5)Co(0.5)Mn(0.5)O(3-delta)was deposited on the electrolyte as the electrode at 700 degrees C in air.
